Summary: NOTE: Unknown object seen over Kleive, Norway on 25 January was a lantern.
divs: Sighting DetailsNOTE: The unknown object, which was seen above Kleive, Norway on 25 January 2009 at 0:40 a.m. was a lantern. This is consistent with the observation of the object. The object was orange, and after a while the light dimmed and went out.
